   "source": [
    "Dataset 2 analysis - This is a dataset from the Western Pennslyvania Regional Data Center that covers the sales of every type of property in the western PA area. I filtered it out to just Pittsburgh neighborhoods and just Estate sales. My data visualization shows the different neighborhoods with their average estate sales."
